data.description: Excellent opportunity to own a duplex one block from bus line, shopping, restaurants & entertainment. Big back yards, bonus rooms, fireplaces, garages, two hall closets on each side. Six parking spots in the driveway, plus on street parking. Some updates include bathrooms, a new furnace, and a water heater on the right side. Broker owns the property.
